title: Steel 4-Wheel Utility Trailer With Wood Deck And Ramps
item_description:
Steel 4-Wheel Utility Trailer With Wood Deck And Ramps

Dimensions

  • Overall Length: 125”
  • Overall Width: 84”
  • Overall Height: 61”
  • Deck Length: 144”
  • Deck Width: 60”
  • Side Height: 12”

Axles, Brakes, and Tires

  • Number of Axles: 2
  • Brake Type: Electric

  • Electric Plug Type: 7-Way Round
  • Hitch: Pintle Hitch

Features

The Bidder shall not bid on behalf of another individual; the Bidder/Purchaser/DMV Registrant must be the same. The Buyer is fully responsible for all aspects of registration, transfer, taxes, and fees due to the DMV.
